{
  "stem": "4226.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some men were tied with their hands in the back, so the tip of their toe was reaching the ground, all their weight.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they would pull them up on some live trees.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They hung them from trees by--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From trees.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they're only 10 meters away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're hanging them up there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and the weight of them were on the shoulder.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They could be conscious up to 10 minutes, and then they lost consciousness.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And their hands-- and the rope from the hands--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The rope from the hand was--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--on the-- pulled up on the tree until the weight-- all their weight was on, on the tip.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were not fully in the air.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Tip on the floor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The tip of their feet touched the ground.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they passed out usually between 10 and 15 minutes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they let them loose.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they poured a bucket or two of cold water over their head, so they revived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And either they let them go, and next day they started again, or they even started-- they put them up straightaway.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I worked in the open, next to the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just cut wood there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was close by.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were not-- they didn't do it in masses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took out one or two at a time, and- and only people which they saw they are rich, or they didn't disclose whatever they had, or, or they had personal--",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's all they wanted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See, there were only two German soldiers there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were more or less in the background.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they probably told them what to do, because two Germans couldn't keep over 2,000 people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had to have Hungarian guards there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
